parameters:
...Hey. For a newbie, you sure did a good job of
embarrassing me.

...Huh!? What do you want, barging into someone's house with
your shoes on!

I've been on this island for 30 years. I can't let a
newcomer woman beat me and lose face as the head of the
exiles!
I've come to punish you! Brace yourself!

\c[27]Number of main acts +1, vaginal ejaculation +1, fellatio +1,
oral ejaculation +1, lewdness level +3\c[0]

*sob*... (It's so frustrating... to be taken advantage of
like this...)

--The men glanced at the exhausted and dazed Karin before
leaving the cabin with satisfied expressions...

That's right. Sorry for making you come all the way to my
cabin...

Being sent to this island has built up my frustration too.
I'm going to crush you all with everything I've got!
Damn it! Don't falter! She's just one woman! Take her down!

Eek! Please forgive me! I swear, I'll never lay a hand on
you again!

...Phew. Good to know you understand. Don't ever come to my
house again.

Ah, yes...! I promise! Do as you like on this island! You
have the head exile's word!
--The heads of the exiles left Karin's cabin bleeding.

(Well, that should teach them a lesson. But more
importantly, how to escape from this island... that's the
real issue...)

--Are you taking a break today? (Recover stamina. One day
passes)

I'm so hungry I can't take it anymore... Maybe I should just
go to sleep for today...

Back when I was in Edo, whenever I got hungry, I'd go to
Oei-san's house and eat lots of dumplings... This is
tough...

--As Karin was about to get into her futon, the door of the
hut opened.
Heheh... Hey, Karin--sorry to bother you at this hour♪

Now, now, don't be so wary. It's just me tonight. You're
hungry, right? Here, have some dried rice.

Oops, I haven't given you permission to eat yet. Of course,
it ain't free. You understand what it means to receive
precious food on this island, right?
食料を受け取る\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

...I don't want it. I'll return this. Even if I'm starving,
I don't want food badly enough to give up my body for it.

Oh? Such noble sentiments despite being hungry. Take care
not to starve to death.
--The head of the exiles left Karin's hut...

--Will you take a rest today? (Recover stamina. One day will
pass.)

--Will you take a rest today? (Stamina recovery. One day
will pass.)
